thread.title_full: New on Amazon Prime: movies, shows added in November

author: Alejandro Alba
title: New on Amazon Prime: movies, shows added in November
text:
Columbia Pictures/Getty Images “The Craft” will be available Nov. 1. 
Amazon will update its Prime and Amazon Video catalog with new movie and TV show titles this November. 
Some of the new TV show and titles that will begin streaming on Nov. 1 include Amazon's original series "Man in the High Castle," season five of "Teen Wolf" and season three of "Vikings." 
Amazon will also add new titles to its Amazon Prime Store, which users can rent or purchase. These are the movies and TV shows that will be available for streaming in November: November 1
